name: MSRI-ONE-GIFPOGV-Y-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-ONE-GIFPOGV-Y-01" Is a single parallel projection artwork. Gif animation of one 3d Object is generated from custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Pink, Orange, Green, Violet. The cells of the Yellow "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the Green loft. The perspective view is drawing maximum details in the resolution of 1024*1024 pixels. Total 128 frames, 1024*1024px canvas.
